<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="home-n">home <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /həʊm/    美 /hoʊm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 家；家庭：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>work from / <strong>at home</strong>
在家办公</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>left home</strong> at the age of 16.
他16岁时离开了家。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 家乡；本国；定居地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She was born in London, but she has <strong>made</strong> Paris her <strong>home</strong>.
她生在伦敦，但在巴黎安了家。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>[常用单数] 发源地；原产地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The home of</strong> the kangaroo is Australia.
袋鼠的原产地是澳大利亚。</p></div>

<h4 id="4c">4.<strong>[C] 疗养院；养育院：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an old people's home
老人之家；养老院</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-home">at home</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在家里；在国内；舒适的；不拘束的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Make yourself at home.
请不要拘束。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>feel at home</strong>
舒适自在</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I began to feel <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ home in the new school when I saw some familiar faces.  （2008 山东改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. at  </p></div>